text: István Grózner (22 July 1955 - 16 September 1993) was a Hungarian equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1955 births Category:1993 deaths Category:Hungarian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Hungary Category:Equestrians at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:People from Zala County
